OL,3,CNo money for pencils and glue sticks-
OL,4,C school finance manager steals #70k
OL,6,FA school finance manager in Nottingham
OL,7,Fhas been jailed for more than two
OL,8,Fyears after abusing her position to
OL,9,Fsteal tens of thousands of pounds.
OL,11,FWendy Gill, who is 61 years-old,
OL,12,Ftransferred more than #70,000 of
OL,13,Fschool funds into her personal bank
OL,14,Faccounts over a six-year period, while
OL,15,Femployed at Bramcote C of E Primary
OL,16,FSchool.
