OL,6,FNottingham Crown Court heard she was
OL,7,Fthe school's business manager and,
OL,8,Famongst other things, had
OL,9,Fresponsibility for managing staff
OL,10,Fpayroll, ordering supplies and
OL,11,Fadministering the school's bank
OL,12,Faccounts.
OL,14,FGill, from Stanton Road, Ilkeston,
OL,15,Fwent on to plead guilty to fraud by
OL,16,Fabuse of position.
OL,18,FWhat happened?
