OL,6,FThe offending came to light in 2022
OL,7,Fwhen governors discovered the school
OL,8,Fwas projected to be in a deficit of
OL,9,F#21,158 ` more than three times the
OL,10,Ffigure Gill had indicated to the head
OL,11,Fteacher.
OL,13,FThe Local Authority began a financial
OL,14,Finvestigation into the school, which
OL,15,Fled to further serious financial
OL,16,Fdiscrepancies being uncovered.
OL,18,FA police investigation was launched
OL,19,Fand Gill was suspended on 20 June 2022.
