OL,4,C school finance manager steals #70k
OL,6,FThe court heard she resigned seven
OL,7,Fdays later.
OL,9,FDetectives analysed Gill's bank
OL,10,Fstatements and discovered #70,581.51
OL,11,Fhad been fraudulently transferred from
OL,12,Fthe school's accounts into three
OL,13,Faccounts belonging to Gill between
OL,14,FApril 2016 and June 2022.
OL,16,FIn a police interview, Gill admitted
OL,17,Fthe allegations against her.
