OL,6,FShe stated she had reasons for
OL,7,Fcommitting the fraud but was not
OL,8,Fprepared to discuss what those reasons
OL,9,Fwere.
OL,11,FThe court heard pupils had to go
OL,12,Fwithout "essential resources" as a
OL,13,Fresult of the financial strain Gill's
OL,14,Factions placed on the school's budget.
OL,16,FAt one point, the school's
OL,17,Fparent`teacher association had to step
OL,18,Fin and buy reading books.
