OL,6,FProsecutors said she was a "well-
OL,7,Fliked" and "trusted" member of staff
OL,8,Fwho repeatedly abused her position.
OL,10,FThe sentencing
OL,12,FAt a sentencing hearing on 10th
OL,13,FSeptember, the school's headteacher
OL,14,FSarah Meredith read out a statement.
