OL,6,FMrs Meredith said: "The biggest impact
OL,7,Fof all has been on the children of the
OL,8,Fschool. We now know that due to the
OL,9,Fdeception and selfish acts of Mrs
OL,10,FGill, the children over a number of
OL,11,Fyears have missed out and suffered
OL,12,Ffrom being unable to access essential
OL,13,Fresources.
OL,15,F"I feel deeply that depriving our
OL,16,Fchildren of this money is totally
OL,17,Fabhorrent. For years as a school we
OL,18,Ftried our very best to give our
OL,19,Fchildren, as our school motto
OL,20,Fadvocates, 'Life In All its Fullness'.
OL,26,@nD@TOUwD@AOU
