OL,4,C school finance manager steals #70k
OL,6,F"However, we were given constant
OL,7,Freminders from Mrs Gill that the
OL,8,Fbudget was 'tight' and we should 'be
OL,9,Fcareful' with our spending. This is
OL,10,Fadvice that we all took on board and
OL,11,Fas a result limited our spending.
OL,13,F"She was trusted by everyone and we
OL,14,Fall believed that the advice she gave
OL,15,Fus was in the best interests of the
OL,16,Fschool, while the children were always
OL,17,Fat the centre of her thinking.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
