OL,6,F"Her mantra was that 'We're the
OL,7,Fbest!'. However, in June 2022 our
OL,8,Ftrust and perception of her was
OL,9,Fcompletely shattered."
OL,11,FThe sentencing hearing heard Gill felt
OL,12,F"utterly ashamed" and is selling her
OL,13,Fhouse to pay back the money she stole.
OL,15,FShe's been jailed for two years and
OL,16,Fone month.
