OL,6,FRecorder James Bide-Thomas said:
OL,7,F"Everyone at Bramcote School feels
OL,8,Fbetrayed. It was plainly a close-knit
OL,9,Fcommunity as shown by the number of
OL,10,Fpeople who have attended court to
OL,11,Fwatch you be sentenced.
OL,13,F"There was no money for new computers,
OL,14,Fnew toys and there was a limit on the
OL,15,Fnumber of pencils and glue sticks that
OL,16,Fcould be purchased.
OL,18,F"Funds to maintain buildings were not
OL,19,Fspent in that fashion, leading to the
OL,20,Fdeterioration of those buildings."
